                  </hi>. I am a pawnbroker, and live in Pitfield-street, Hox<lb></lb>ton. I produce a pillow, which I received from a woman whom I do not recollect, on the 7th of December, for 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MRS. COOPER</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> All these articles are mine, and these are tickets I found.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Sarah Haddon.</hi> There was but one sheet in the lodging, and we never had a table-cloth.</p>
